          +-----------------------+
          |   Start Pipeline      |
          +-----------------------+
                     |
                     v
          +-----------------------+
          |   Clone Repo Stage    |
          | git pull from GitHub  |
          +-----------------------+
                     |
                     v
          +-----------------------+
          |    Build Stage        |
          | mvn clean package     |
          | (skip tests)          |
          +-----------------------+
                     |
                     v
          +-----------------------+
          |    Run App Stage      |
          | Stop old process      |
          | Run JAR on port 9090  |
          | Logs -> app.log       |
          +-----------------------+
                     |
                     v
          +-----------------------+
          |      Post Actions     |
          |  Success: Echo msg    |
          |  Failure: Echo msg    |
          +-----------------------+
                     |
                     v
          +-----------------------+
          |      Pipeline Ends    |
          +-----------------------+

